      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "Add live waveform + inline transcription, fix mobile ribbon label, release 0.3.0\n\n- Live recording waveform (status bar on desktop, floating pill on mobile),\n  reading the existing analyser node exposed via RecorderController.getAnalyser().\n- Inline transcription at the cursor: new toggle/start/stop commands insert the\n  transcript where the cursor is and append a footnote linking back to the\n  recording ([^id] renders as a superscript reference).\n- Mobile ribbon menu now reflects recording state: update the internal ribbon\n  item title (mobile rebuilds its menu from it) and swap the mic/stop icon.\n- Add public ROADMAP.md; condense README; document the Obsidian 1.13.0\n  requirement (settings tab uses the 1.13.0 getSettingDefinitions API).",
      "downloadCount": 2,
