      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "Migrates the settings tab off the deprecated display() override onto Obsidian's declarative getSettingDefinitions() API (bumps minAppVersion to 1.13.0). Also fixes several correctness and release-hygiene issues: drops versions.json from release assets (Obsidian reads it from the repo, not release assets), narrows error handling from `any` to `unknown` with proper message extraction, replaces a `document` reference with `activeDocument` so the mic-disconnect notice works correctly in popout windows, and removes unnecessary type assertions and an unused import.\n\nNo user-facing behavior change; settings UI and functionality are unchanged from 0.2.0.",
      "downloadCount": 1,
      "draft": false,
